{"title":"The Allygn EdelMü Lamp Comes in Colors","link":"https://theradavist.com/the-allygn-edelmu-lamp-comes-in-colors","date":1772637667000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>The <a href=\"https://fern-bicycles.myshopify.com/en-us/products/allygn-edelmu?variant=52942813135115\" target=\"_blank\">Allygn EdelMü</a>, designed by Berlin’s Florian Haeussler of <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/fern-cycles\" target=\"_blank\">Fern Cycles</a> now comes in a few anodized colors…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Allygn EdelMü is a dynamo taillight that combines the best of two worlds, matching the iconic design of the famous SON Edelux headlight with the high-tech internals of the Busch &amp; Müller Mü. It’s available in two versions: direct-mount for M6 braze-ons on the seat tube and standard ring-mount for M3 bolts, which works perfectly with the Drust Cycles rear light mounts. Braze-on parts and adapters are available separately.</p>\n<p>This is the ring mount version, <a href=\"https://fern-bicycles.myshopify.com/en-us/products/drust-rear-light-mount\" target=\"_blank\">which can be used with the Drust light mount</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Fern-Allygn-Edelmu-Colors-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sleek design matches the iconic SON Edelux headlights</li>\n<li>Busch &amp; Müller electronics with capacitors for long stand light duration</li>\n<li>Robust CNC-machined aluminium housing with great side visibility due to safety cut-outs</li>\n<li>Comes with 6V AC dynamo internals, but 5-15V DC Mü internals can be fitted too</li>\n<li>Ring mount version works perfect with Drust cycles rear light mount, available as special bundle deal</li>\n<li>Frame builder braze-ons available</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://fern-bicycles.myshopify.com/en-us/products/allygn-edelmu?variant=52942813135115\" target=\"_blank\">Allygn</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/the-allygn-edelmu-lamp-comes-in-colors\">The Allygn EdelMü Lamp Comes in Colors</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://cms.theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"bb0574b250727cdbf63aa091feed3b1a7b8a876cde55d3cd94dc548b1a4ad8c3","category":"Cycling"}